text: Santiago Cañete (born 18 December 1935) is a Spanish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Spain Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from the Province of Albacete
